      "title": "[IIP-39] Update IDLE distribution, Steakhouse USDC as a new USDC BY yield source, transfer USDC to see the IDLE-USDC pool, transfer M2-2024 budget",
      "content": "The following is an extract of the proposal posted on the [Idle governance forum](https://gov.idle.finance/t/iip-39-update-idle-distribution-steakhouse-usdc-as-a-new-usdc-by-yield-source-transfer-usdc-to-see-the-idle-usdc-pool-transfer-m2-2024-budget/1255).\n\n### Summary\nThe IIP aims to pause the Liquidity Mining program, formalize the strategic round agreement with Rockway X, update the USDC Best Yield‚Äôs vault underlying markets, seed a new IDLE pool launch on Uniswap, and transfer the M2-2024 budget to Leagues.\n\n## Rationale\n### 1. IDLE incentives distribution update\nThe DAO agreed to pause the Liquidity Mining program that has been distributing IDLE to users since 2021\n\n> ### Pause the Liquidity Mining program\n>\n>One option is to pause the Liquidity Mining distribution\n>\n> * From 250 to 0 IDLE/day\n>\n> From a DAO treasury perspective, this option would stop the emission of IDLE and reduce the selling pressure on the DAO governance token.\n> \n> Given the current low emission, the yields of BY vaults would be minimally affected. A possible downside of this pause is linked to the integrators that rely on IDLE rewards. To adjust this the DAO may update the [Integrators program](https://docs.idle.finance/products/get-involved/integrators-program) and create ad-hoc solutions for partners that count on the additional return given by IDLE.\n\n### 2. Strategic round with Rockway X\nIn light of the recent round closure, the parties agreed not to transfer/vest any IDLE tokens to the investor. The DAO tokens will be kept in the long-term reward fund.\n\nRockwayX will transfer the stablecoin to the Idle DAO‚Äôs fee treasury in 2 tranches\n\n> **Agreement Terms**\n> The terms of the agreement remain largely unchanged, except for the investment structure. The investment will now occur in two tranches of $500,000 each with the second tranche tied to $50M TVL milestone, as partly mentioned in our previous update [here](https://gov.idle.finance/t/iip-39-update-idle-distribution-transfer-idle-to-vesting-contract-steakhouse-usdc-as-a-new-usdc-by-yield-source-transfer-usdc-to-see-the-idle-usdc-pool/1250/2). The first $500,000 tranche has been already deposited into the [Fee Treasury](https://etherscan.io/address/0x69a62c24f16d4914a48919613e8ee330641bcb94#tokentxns) controlled by Idle DAO.\n\n> This proposal is meant to formalize the funding round and strategic agreement between Idle DAO and [Rockaway X ](https://rockawayx.com/) to solidify the relationship as liquidity providers and users of our product suite and pave the way for a new line of institutional-grade yield products.\n\n> This funding round provides the following:\n> \n> * Rockaway X will allocate 1,000,000 USDC (or other stablecoins) to Idle DAO‚Äôs Fee Treasury.\n> * Idle DAO will allocate 1,733,333 IDLE from the Idle DAO‚Äôs [Long Term Fund ](https://etherscan.io/address/0x107a369bc066c77ff061c7d2420618a6ce31b925) to Rockaway X Vesting Contract.\n> \n> IDLE tokens taken from Long Term Fund will be subject to a 2-year vesting period, with 33% released after a 12-month cliff and the rest with a 12-month block-by-block linear vesting.\n\n### 3. Steakhouse vault as new yield source for USDC BY\nThe Steakhouse Senior Tranche will be added as a new yield source to the USDC Best Yield vault. \n\n> Following the [M1-2024 roadmap](https://gov.idle.finance/t/leagues-m1-2024-roadmap-and-m4-2023-recap/1231), Idle DAO Leagues has initiated the process of revamping the Best Yield vaults. This process counts on multiple steps:\n> \n> 1. Unwind the Junior Best Yield vaults\n> 2. Renew the BY underlying yield sources to offer the best yield-optimized offering in the market\n> \n> This post aims to expand on the second step listed and specifically focuses on the USDC Best Yield market.\n\nThe vault will improve the yield of the USDC BY vault while having a safe risk score of B.\n\n### 4. AMM liquidity improvements\nTo improve the IDLE liquidity in the markets, the DAO decided to follow these steps (2/3 already completed). In light of the recent round closed and the new agreement terms, Leagues advise reducing the liquidity increase by half, i.e. $75k, to ensure enough working capital to achieve the next steps in the roadmap. \n\n> The DAO has shared his preferences about the next steps for the IDLE AMM liquidity improvements:\n> \n> * Migrate the 8020 IDLE pool to Uniswap v3\n> * Launch an IDLE-USDC pool on Uniswap v3\n> * Bootstrap the pool with $150,000 of DAO‚Äôs treasury\n\n### 5. M2-2024 Leagues budget\nThis IIP will be used also to transfer the M2-2024 budget that has been pending since the DAO vote. \n\n> ## Leagues M2-2024 Expected Budget\n> \n>  ![image](ipfs://bafkreicmhhik444vlg6knxvkjuby7xtw65vf3534hmwzcqwljiqg7guio4)\n>   \n> \n> **The [expected budget for M2-2024 ](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1w1KJkc3c6BW2N7zfmh9RCg0OcHZPdfiL3D2tTVfK9bI/edit?usp=sharing) is $148‚Äô015 in stablecoin and 66‚Äô490 IDLE (using a 20-day rolling price at the time of writing).**\n> \n> At the time of writing, the [Treasury League multisig](https://app.safe.global/balances?safe=eth:0xFb3bD022D5DAcF95eE28a6B07825D4Ff9C5b3814) stablecoin or equivalents holdings currently stand at $55‚Äô343 in stablecoins (excluding $129‚Äô353 in ETH/WBTC/altcoins, using price at the current time) so if the Temperature Check for IDLE tokenholders is positive, $92‚Äô672 funds will be transferred from the [Fee Treasury](https://etherscan.io/address/0x69a62c24f16d4914a48919613e8ee330641bcb94) (in either one or two installments), and 66‚Äô490 IDLE will be transferred from the [Ecosystem Fund](https://etherscan.io/address/0xb0aa1f98523ec15932dd5faac5d86e57115571c7) via the next IIP.\n\n## Specifications\nThe code of the IIP-39 can be found on GitHub [here](https://github.com/Idle-Finance/idle-proposals/blob/main/scripts/iip-39.ts#L86-L99) and consists of 5 actions.\n\nIIP-39 actions:\n\n* 1 action to set the Liquidity Mining distribution, `_setIdleRate`, from 250 to 0 IDLE/day\n* 1 action to perform the last claim of all unclaimed IDLE for the Best Yields vault\n* 1 action to replace the cp_POR_USDC Senior Tranche with the Steakhouse USDC Senior Tranche in the Best Yield USDC vault\n* 1 action to transfer $75,000 equivalent in stablecoin from the Fee Treasury to the Treasury multisig wallet to seed the new IDLE-USDC pool on Uniswap*\n* 1 action to transfer $148,000 equivalent in stablecoin from the Fee Treasury and 66,490 IDLE from the Ecosystem fund to the Treasury multisig wallet to fund the Leagues‚Äô budget for M2-2024*\n\nWhere the Steakhouse wrapper contract address is:\n\n* Steakhouse USDC Senior tranche `0x96Dd27112bDd615c3A2D649fe22d8eE27e448152`\n\n*Please note that the above actions concerning stablecoin transfers will be merged in the IIP code.",
